---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const post = {
  title: 'Welcome to the ICN Blog',
  date: '2024-07-26',
  author: 'The ICN Team',
};
---

<Layout
  title={post.title + " | ICN Blog"}
  description={`Read the blog post titled "${post.title}" by ${post.author} on the InterCooperative Network blog.`}
>
  <article class="pt-32 pb-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-3xl">

      <header class="mb-8">
        <span class="bg-accent-primary/20 text-accent-primary border border-accent-primary/30 text-sm font-bold px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-4 inline-block">
          ANNOUNCEMENT
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 leading-tight text-white">{post.title}</h1>
        <p class="text-slate-gray text-lg">
          Posted on {new Date(post.date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })} by {post.author}
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-light-slate leading-relaxed">
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">
          Welcome to the official blog of the InterCooperative Network (ICN). We're launching this space
          to share development updates, technical insights, and community news.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-white">What is ICN?</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          ICN is a substrate daemon for the cooperative internet. It provides infrastructure for:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong class="text-white">Timebanks:</strong> Hour-for-hour exchange systems with mutual credit ledgers</li>
          <li><strong class="text-white">Mutual Credit:</strong> Community currencies backed by mutual trust</li>
          <li><strong class="text-white">Democratic Governance:</strong> Built-in proposals, voting, and CCL contracts</li>
          <li><strong class="text-white">Federation:</strong> Networks of cooperatives with maintained local autonomy</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-white">Current Status</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          ICN has completed 20 development phases with 1,134+ tests passing. The system includes:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>16 specialized Rust crates</li>
          <li>DIDs with Ed25519 cryptography</li>
          <li>Web-of-participation trust graph</li>
          <li>QUIC/TLS secure networking</li>
          <li>Mutual credit ledger with Merkle-DAG anchoring</li>
          <li>Pilot Web UI for cooperative communities</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-white">What's Next: Track C1</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          The next milestone is Track C1: Pilot Deployment. We're seeking cooperative communities
          interested in running real-world pilots of ICN for timebanking, mutual credit, or
          cooperative governance.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-8">
          If you're part of a cooperative, timebank, or community organization interested in
          piloting ICN, please reach out via our <a href="https://discord.gg/GCWKPWdvgH" class="text-accent-primary hover:underline">Discord</a>
          or <a href="https://github.com/InterCooperative-Network/icn/discussions" class="text-accent-primary hover:underline">GitHub Discussions</a>.
        </p>

        <hr class="my-8 border-slate-600"/>

        <p class="text-center">
          <a href="/blog" class="text-accent-primary hover:underline font-semibold">&larr; Back to Blog</a>
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </article>

  <!-- Call to Action Section -->
  <section class="bg-midnight-navy/50 border-t border-slate-600 py-12">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Ready to Get Started?</h3>
      <p class="text-light-slate mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Clone the repository, run the tests, and explore ICN's capabilities.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/get-started" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 bg-accent-primary text-midnight-navy font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-accent-primary/90 transition-colors">
          Get Started
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/InterCooperative-Network/icn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 bg-transparent border-2 border-accent-primary text-accent-primary font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-accent-primary hover:text-midnight-navy transition-colors">
          View Source
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
